channel.title: DevotionScape Devolpment Team
channel.description:
Hello, I am starting a server called DevotionScape.
*
What do I have so far? I have a vB forum, and a normal PI Client and source.
The source has basic editing done, but I am looking for a team to help me with this project.
Why? I, myself am not the best coder, and due to school I am not on as much, but when I am on, I do my best to work on the forums and server.
Reward: Admin spot in-game, and programmer rank on forums.
Application: Name Age Expirance What can you bring to us?
Regards, Pimple.
